📊 Part 3 — Monitor CPU & Watch ASG Scale:
              Step 1 — Go to Monitoring Tab:
                         Go to EC2 → Auto Scaling Groups
                         Select Demo-ASG
                         Click "Monitoring" tab
                         Click "EC2" sub-tab
                         💡 You will see the CPU Utilization graph spike toward 100%
                         CPU Utilization
                         100% ┤                    ████████████████
                          80% ┤               █████
                          60% ┤          ██████
                          40% ┤─ ─ ─ ─ ─ Target Line ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─
                          20% ┤ ████
                           0% ┼──────────────────────────────────
                              Time →
                                    (stress starts)   (ASG scales out)
              Step 2 — Watch New Instance Launch:
                          Click "Activity" tab in Demo-ASG
                          You will see a new entry:
                          Status:      Successful ✅
                          Description: Launching a new EC2 instance: i-0zzzzzzzzz
                          Cause:       Target tracking policy triggered
                                       (Average CPU Utilization = 100% > Target 40%)
              Step 3 — Verify 3 Instances Are Healthy:
                         Go to EC2 → Target Groups
                         Select demo-tg-alb → "Targets" tab
                         
                         Instance	Launched By	Health Status
                         i-0xxxxxxxxxx	ASG	✅ Healthy
                         i-0yyyyyyyyyy	ASG	✅ Healthy
                         i-0zzzzzzzzz	ASG (new — stress triggered)	✅ Healthy
              Step 4 — Stop Stress & Watch Scale In:
                        Go back to the EC2 terminal
                        Press Ctrl + C to stop the stress test
                        Wait 5–10 minutes
                        ASG will detect CPU dropped below 40% → terminate the extra instance
                        Activity Tab — Scale In:
                        Status:      Successful ✅
                        Description: Terminating EC2 instance: i-0zzzzzzzzz
                        Cause:       Target tracking policy — CPU < 40%
                                     (Cooldown period expired)
